data.description: Experience the benefits of OWNED SOLAR in this fantastic 3 bed, 2 bath residence! Nestled near the Garden Hwy Bike Trail, it's a mere two-block stroll to the Sacramento River. Enjoy quick access to Downtown, Shopping, the Freeway, UC Davis, and the Airport. Inside, discover granite countertops, captivating laminate floors, and an inviting floor plan. The property boasts a smart watering system, eliminating the hassle of remembering to turn off the water on rainy days. Discover a home that combines convenience, style, and energy efficiency!
